  "description": "Replaces the Totem of Undying with a watch.",
  "body": "---\n<p align=\"center\"?>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/watch-of-undying\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bf84aa11b4afd69cdbd20a199bc6d93c50fac58b.png\" \n        alt=\"Modrinth\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        url=\"modrinth.com\"\n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/watch-of-undying\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3531508338997863e0b15c2252d16bf51ceb5669.png\" \n        alt=\"Curseforge\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/watch-of-undying\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eac8caa46edda35d821be9a2e1a8e16a00a9cadc.png\" \n        alt=\"Planet Minecraft\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n</p>  \n\n---\nThis resource pack replaces the Totem of Undying with a watch that your character wears. It also makes it invisible in first person. Doesn't require Optifine or any other mods.\n\n![Before/After (Third person)](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yhG3oUCc/images/9f816d6b597810f1666c4000a5bfa6b3495dde33.png)\n![Before/After (First person)](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/yhG3oUCc/images/918b9b085d449c41b96219a1216c6ca80eea4e0d.png)\n\n---",
